{"tid":2340792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人投訴惠州隔離酒店 保安擸棍談判","createTime":"2020-12-25T19:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T08:21:24.000Z","uid":271829,"like":449,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"b5f8dc8b734ad4da7325b7400ed2689b55fc0c72","tid":2340792,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T19:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gefqkMlMKclA7ZvxFwesruEsbf4=/1181x1300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7RER3NCRANDKZFBE3CWCRZMDIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgefqkMlMKclA7ZvxFwesruEsbf4%3D%2F1181x1300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7RER3NCRANDKZFBE3CWCRZMDIA.jpg&h=d05df18c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聯署信指一名女童跌傷流血，惟酒店遲遲不安排她送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n自第四波疫情爆發，港人趁聖誕長假期北上「避疫」過新年的人數陸續增多，有自稱是「愛國愛港大聯盟」的微信公眾號「中港大聯盟」，昨日發文指60多名到廣東惠州隔離的港人，聯名向惠州市委書記李貽偉致投訴信，指位於龍門縣的隔離酒店「天然居」收費貴、食物有蒼蠅、小童跌傷無妥善處理，更指住客與酒店職員交涉時「酒店負責人大聲吼叫，且多名保安人員持一人高警棍與我們談判」。惟本報昨晚發現，該篇文章已被刪除，原因是「接相關投訴，此內容違反《中華人民共和國網絡安全法》」。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/ODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI%2F&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQL9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=5ff2c391\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI%2F&h=c341e9d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/ODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI/</a>"},{"pid":"dbdf554dd8837b3ec88143d56ee28d5b7b8dab17","tid":2340792,"uid":253016,"like":398,"dislike":18,"score":380,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T19:28:50.000Z","msg":"港咩人呀垃圾蘋果<br />\n支那殖民就正名支那豬<br />\n又偷偷地滲透大支那主義"},{"pid":"54ac97bca7d06aa0246cf7a5c5c0afe99c741057","tid":2340792,"uid":152589,"like":76,"dislike":3,"scor